    <published>2016-01-13T00:00:00Z</published>
    <link href="http://www.mapdb.org/blog/mapdb3.html" />
    <author>
      <name>Jan Kotek</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;I will start with the bad news. Current 2.0 branch needs major redesign. It has bugs, concurrency issues and is slow. I decided to start work on new 3.0 branch. First milestone with HTreeMap will be released in a few days, stable version will be out on March.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
