  <entry xml:base="http://www.mapdb.org/blog/atom.xml">
    <title type="text">2.0-beta6 released (2015-08-18)</title>
    <id>http://www.mapdb.org/changelog.html#beta6-released-2015-08-18</id>
    <updated>2015-08-18T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <published>2015-08-18T00:00:00Z</published>
    <link href="http://www.mapdb.org/changelog.html#beta6-released-2015-08-18" />
    <author>
      <name>Jan Kotek</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;There is &lt;strong&gt;storage format change&lt;/strong&gt;: array hashing has changed. If you use any array such as &lt;code class=&quot;docutils literal&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pre&quot;&gt;Object[]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code class=&quot;docutils literal&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pre&quot;&gt;byte[]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;,
&lt;code class=&quot;docutils literal&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pre&quot;&gt;long[]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;, etc... as key in &lt;code class=&quot;docutils literal&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;pre&quot;&gt;HashMap&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt; it is not readable in new version.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
